<servinfosub id = "AENCP70A8204008001">
<title>
Scan Tool Data Definition
</title>
<topic id = "AENCP70A8204008002">
<title>
System ID (4ch / 8ch / 9ch)
</title>
<ptxt>
This parameter indicates number of initiator circuits.
</ptxt>
</topic>
<topic id = "AENCP70A8204008003">
<title>
Battery Voltage (V)
</title>
<ptxt>
Power supply voltage is an analog input signal read by SDM.
</ptxt>
</topic>
<topic id = "AENCP70A8204008004">
<title>
Backup Volt (V)
</title>
<ptxt>
This parameter indicates capacity of backup capacitor installed to maintain ignition current (as much as possible) even when power supply to SDM that ignites inflator is shut off.
</ptxt>
</topic>
<topic id = "AENCP70A8204008005">
<title>
Driv A/B Ini Res (Driver air bag initiator resistance) (ohm)
</title>
<ptxt>
This parameter indicates resistance of driver air bag initiator circuit.
</ptxt>
</topic>
<topic id = "AENCP70A8204008006">
<title>
Pass A/B Ini Res (Passenger air bag initiator resistance) (ohm)
</title>
<ptxt>
This parameter indicates resistance of passenger air bag initiator circuit.
</ptxt>
</topic>
<topic id = "AENCP70A8204008007">
<title>
Driv Preten Ini Res (Driver pretensioner initiator resistance) (ohm)
</title>
<ptxt>
This parameter indicates resistance of driver seat belt pretensioner initiator circuit.
</ptxt>
</topic>
<topic id = "AENCP70A8204008008">
<title>
Pass Preten Ini Res (Passenger pretensioner initiator resistance) (ohm)
</title>
<ptxt>
This parameter indicates resistance of passenger seat belt pretensioner initiator circuit.
</ptxt>
</topic>
<topic id = "AENCP70A8204008009">
<title>
Driv Sidebag Ini Res (Driver side air-bag initiator resistance) (ohm)
</title>
<ptxt>
This parameter indicates resistance of driver-side side-air bag initiator circuit.
</ptxt>
</topic>
<topic id = "AENCP70A8204008010">
<title>
Pass Sidebag Ini Res (Passenger side-air bag initiator resistance) (ohm)
</title>
<ptxt>
This parameter indicates resistance of passenger-side side-air bag initiator circuit.
</ptxt>
</topic>
<topic id = "AENCP70A8204008011">
<title>
Driv Curtain Ini Res (Driver-side curtain air bag initiator resistance) (ohm)
</title>
<ptxt>
This parameter indicates resistance of driver-side curtain air bag initiator circuit.
</ptxt>
</topic>
<topic id = "AENCP70A8204008012">
<title>
Pass Curtain Ini Res (Passenger-side curtain air bag initiator resistance) (ohm)
</title>
<ptxt>
This parameter indicates resistance of passenger-side curtain air bag initiator circuit.
</ptxt>
</topic>
<topic id = "AENCP70A8204008013">
<title>
Knee Squib Res (Knee air bag initiator resistance) (ohm)
</title>
<ptxt>
This parameter indicates the resistance of the knee air bag initiator circuit.
</ptxt>
</topic>
